wl xliii and losing super bowl xxx and super bowl xlv the team currently competes in the north division of the american football conference afc key to color coding of list of seasons table nfl champions super bowl champions present conference champions division champions wild card berth one game playoff berth season team league conference division regular season postseason results awards finish won lost ties pct pittsburgh pirates nfl east th nfl east th nfl east rd nfl east nd nfl east rd nfl east th nfl east th t pittsburgh steelers nfl east th nfl east th nfl east nd steagles nfl east rd card pitt nfl east th pittsburgh steelers nfl east th nfl east rd t bill dudley joe f carr trophy mvp nfl east nd lost eastern divisional playoff eagles nfl east rd t nfl east nd nfl american rd t nfl american th nfl american th nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern th t nfl eastern rd nfl eastern rd nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern nd lost playoff bowl lions exhibition gm nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern th nfl eastern century th nfl eastern century th nfl eastern century th joe greene defensive rookie of the year nfl afc central rd nfl afc central nd nfl afc central st won divisional playoffs raiders lost conference championship dolphins chuck noll afc coach of the year franco harris offensive rookie of the year joe greene defensive player of the year franco harris afc offensive rookie of the year nfl afc central nd lost divisional playoffs raiders nfl afc central st won divisional playoffs bills won conference championship raiders won super bowl ix vikings jack lambert defensive rookie of the year joe greene defensive player of the year franco harris super bowl mvp nfl afc central st won divisional playoffs colts won conference championship raiders won super bowl x cowboys mel blount defensive player of the year lynn swann super bowl mvp nfl afc central st won divisional playoffs colts lost conference champions